{"tid":1793600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"談杯葛消費成果","createTime":"2019-12-22T13:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T17:56:26.000Z","uid":26770,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f61f692ceb74ccb3253f8f550f432915967993f8","tid":1793600,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:34:48.000Z","msg":"政府已經搵打手講食肆的環境同往年差不多<br />\n但團年飯,大年大節的飯局係香港傳統好少會唔攪<br />\n<br />\n<ins>而最值得睇的係鞋,衣物,海味鋪的環境係差到嚇死人</ins><br />\n而香港過年就係全年收入的重大部分<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔攪死香港個市港共政權絕對唔會交出強姦,殺害市民的警魔</span>"},{"pid":"f2b6253f9e8f3a6793561be4948a00dc1d6723dc","tid":1793600,"uid":10788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:35:20.000Z","msg":"香港獨立，唯一出路"},{"pid":"6d683796c4e037021bdb53d459dfc3d4d90774f3","tid":1793600,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:42:47.000Z","msg":"同埋食肆個環境其實都係差<br />\n好少鋪做到第二轉客<br />\n<br />\n仲有部分鋪第一轉照開比散客食特價邊爐,姐係無booking客"},{"pid":"440b7e732f0f9c145330e9202bc796c991b1cae1","tid":1793600,"uid":20262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:46:35.000Z","msg":"香港人 比心機罷食啦"},{"pid":"19bfa502e83717eac2ca242d50c699836c4d0e4a","tid":1793600,"uid":37330,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:20:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">全城sales出盡奶力推銷</span></span><br />\n今日行過兩個大型商場<br />\n全部商店大折扣<br />\n個個都開開心心 有折狗衝<br />\n一袋兩袋<br />\n完全唔記得已死去嘅手足<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁多個月 為乜呀</span></span><br />\n買少陣嘢得唔得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">爭氣啦 香港人</span></span><br />\n只有經濟壓力先可以憾動呢個政權"},{"pid":"cb51e098829c1892261c9231b6e4937255cd754f","tid":1793600,"uid":37330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:21:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港唔可以輸嫁啦</span>"},{"pid":"316008b655c2bad505d7cb88